296
00:18:49,058 --> 00:18:50,458
Luckily, the truth came out,

297
00:18:50,698 --> 00:18:52,099
and the groom called the police.

298
00:18:53,179 --> 00:18:54,778
That's outrageous. Let me see.

299
00:18:56,058 --> 00:18:57,099
That's ridiculous.

300
00:18:57,419 --> 00:18:59,099
She isn't afraid of being found out.

301
00:18:59,179 --> 00:19:00,579
Yeah.

302
00:19:00,819 --> 00:19:02,139
It's so dramatic.

303
00:19:02,379 --> 00:19:03,218
Right.

304
00:19:04,298 --> 00:19:04,738
Stop.

305
00:19:06,218 --> 00:19:07,099
What's wrong?

306
00:19:09,339 --> 00:19:10,498
Nothing.

307
00:19:11,419 --> 00:19:12,619
This person

308
00:19:14,498 --> 00:19:16,258
