I'm honored to have my great partner,

481
00:28:16,978 --> 00:28:19,899
Ms. Xu Yan, the main planner
of Family Feast,

482
00:28:20,058 --> 00:28:22,419
to discuss
hot social issues with us here.

483
00:28:27,778 --> 00:28:30,018
Recently, I came across a news report.

484
00:28:30,218 --> 00:28:32,698
